                Thus, merely having a website could put you a step ahead of your competition. A site is one more way to be driving more customers, revenue, and overall value to your business.</p><h3>Top Ways A Website Benefits A Company</h3><br><p class="card-text"></p><div class="card-image-box d-flex">    <div class="col-lg-6">        <img src="https://broadly.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/Benefits-of-websites-for-companies.jpeg" alt="blog-image">    </div><!-- end col-lg-6 -->    </div>
                <p class="card-text">Here are twenty-two of the top benefits of having a website for your small business, along with some ideas on how to get the most out of it:</p>
                <br>
                <h3>1. Look Professional</h3>
                <br>
                <p class="card-text">
